NB. normalize
NB. normalize vertices to centered at origin and unit radius.
normalize=: 3 : 0
v=. y -"1 (+/ % #) y
v=. v % >./ +/ &. (*:"_) "1 v
clean v
)

NB. tetrahedron
tetrahedron=: 3 : 0
m=: 2 1 o."1 0 o. 0 2 4 % 3
